For our New Maker @alannasapwell , creating the ideal pairing is all about balance. "Veuve Clicquot Yellow Label has depth and freshness all rolled into one. I wanted to bring those same layers to this dish to enhance the flavours of the champagne." Click on the link in bio to discover her recipe and try it at home!
#LiveClicquot #NewMaker

Discover the exchange between Fatoumata Ly, Sista x Bold mentor,  co-founder of You're Welcome and VP of Singa France, and Céline Favy Huin, founder of Feel Object. 

Sista x Bold is a support programme created in May 2020 by @SISTA and Maison @VeuveClicquot to help women entrepreneurs recover from the effects of the global pandemic, preserve their businesses, and look to the future with confidence.

Thank you @fatouly and @celinefavyhuin for sharing your experience! For more inspiring stories, click on our link in bio. 
#veuveclicquotxwomen #sistabold #sista #wearesista 
.
.

Episode 10 of our series The Ride takes us to the heart of Veuve Clicquot's chalk cellars in Reims where time is luxury. Called Les Crayères, these former chalk quarries were bought by the Maison at the beginning of the 20th century and provide the perfect conditions for aging our wines. Watch as Marie, winemaker, and Lison, wine educator take us through the process step by step. Discover all the episodes of The Ride to find out more and let us know what you'd like to learn about next!

.
